Camoflage::

She sat crying in bot mode. "Please, why *sob* won't someone help 
us?"  She put a hand on KitKat's shoulder, "I'm so *sob* sorry. But 
they can't hear me I guess."

KitKat::
She moaned as her mech fluid levels dropped again. She lifted her 
head up and whispered, "It's alright, we must all greet the matrix at 
sometime. Thank ou for all that you have...."  She passed out.

Camoflage::

She started crying harder and whailing. She shook KitKat's body, "No, 
please don't go. I don't want to be alone out here again. No please."

KitKat::
She was alive, but in dire need of medical attention.
